| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5608 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a491a4fa-da7a-5460-bc67-8b1a5d755af9"
